metadata.title: Nidhish Alex - Founder - Stealth Startup | LinkedIn
metadata.description:
Creator of Contentop, One of the World's GenAI Pioneers. · Nidhish Alex is the Founder and Chief Engineer of Contentop, the world's first commercial generative AI technology. He established Contentop in 2015, and the technology can autonomously generate content. Nidhish holds a postgraduate degree in Computational Linguistics (also known as Natural Language Processing) and Knowledge Engineering, which he earned in the pre-AI era in 2008. 

In 2018, Nidhish Alex developed the Adzis content engine, which utilizes AI to create videos, images, and various other types of content which later inspired many new-gen Generative AI companies. · Experience: Stealth Startup · Education: College of Engineering, Guindy · Location: Chennai · 500+ connections on LinkedIn. View Nidhish Alex’s profile on LinkedIn, a professional community of 1 billion members.
